      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ Gas 7</p><p>Rinse the <strong>sushi rice</strong> in a sieve under <strong>cold running water</strong> for 30 secs (use your hands to really wash the grains!), then set aside to drain fully</p><p>Add the <strong>drained rice</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to a gentle boil over a high heat</p>",
